39
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:37,140
<b>Starfell Lake</b>

40
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:21,525
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Ooh! Did you just feel the elements of the world?</i>

41
00:06:21,570 --> 00:06:26,130
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Seems all you had to do was just touch the statue and you got the power of Anemo!</i>

42
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:31,550
