00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:32,600
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Just what was that? Paimon thought we were gonna get eaten.</i>

67
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:38,350
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>It definitely has something to do with that weirdo who was talking to the dragon...</i>

68
00:09:38,401 --> 00:09:38,800
<b>Pasichnik:</b> I can't belive dragons exist in this world...

69
00:09:38,826 --> 00:09:41,350
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Yeah, Paimon gets why you're worried...</i>

70
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:44,150
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Oh? What's that?</i>

71
00:09:45,050 --> 00:09:49,300
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>There's some kind of shiny red thingy on the big rock over there...</i>

72
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:51,00
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Let's go take a closer look.</i>

