00:10:05,385 --> 00:10:10,950
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>All Paimon knows is that it's dangerous. Best we put it away for now.</i>

76
00:10:11,573 --> 00:10:14,750
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Okay, we've got it! Now let's get out of here.</i>

77
