<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Hey, you! Stop right there!</font>

78
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:46,650
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">May the Anemo God protect you, stranger!</font>

79
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:52,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">I am Amber, Outrider for the Knights of Favonius.</font>

80
00:10:52,050 --> 00:10:56,450
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">You don't look like citizens of Mondstadt. Explain yourselves!</font> 

81
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:59,500
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>We're not looking for trouble.</i>

82
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:02,050
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">That's what all the troublemakers say.</font>

83
00:11:02,250 --> 00:11:03,200
<b>Pasichnik:</b> Hello, I'm Pasichnik.

84
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:06,250
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">...Doesn't sound like a local name to me.</font>

85
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:09,900
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">And this... mascot, what's the deal with it?</font>

