00:11:09,930 --> 00:11:11,115
<b>Pasichnik:</b> Emeergency food. (Пасічник, Паймон же тобі довіряла!)

87
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:15,500
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Hey! That's even worse than being a mascot!</i>

89
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:19,350
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">So to sum it up, you're traveling partners, right?</font>

90
00:11:19,450 --> 00:11:26,600
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Well look, there's been a large dragon sighted around Mondstadt recently. Best you get inside the city as soon as possible.</font> 

91
00:11:26,850 --> 00:11:29,450
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">It's not far from here, I'll escort you there.</font> 

92
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:34,950
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Oh? Aren't you here for some other reason?</i>

93
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:39,250
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">I am. But not to worry, I can keep you both safe while doing that too.</font>

94
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:43,900
