00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:44,500
<b>Pasichnik:</b> Why so suspicious?

96
00:11:44,523 --> 00:11:49,650
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Oh, ahh... I'm sorry. probably not something I should say as a knight.</font>

97
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:56,145
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">I give oyu my apologies, uh... strange yet... respectable travelers.</font>

98
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:58,450
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>That sounded so fake!</i>

99
00:11:58,581 --> 00:12:05,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Do you have something against the type of language usage prescribed by the Knights of Favonius Handbook!?</font> 

