00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:39,300
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Oh, looking for your family... Huh.</font>

107
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:42,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Ah...</font> 

108
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:47,150
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Okay! Let me finish my other stuff first, and then I can help you put up posters around the city...</font>

