<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">These monsters have been getting too close to the city recently.</font>

114
00:13:20,650 --> 00:13:23,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">My task this time is to clear out their <b>camp</b>.</font>

115
00:13:54,450 --> 00:13:55,950
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Heh, nothing to it.</font> 

116
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:59,900
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Though I've gotta say, you surprised me a little with your moves there...</font>

117
