<b>Paimon:</b> <i>These creatures don't seem like the type to set up camp so close to cities like this.</i>

121
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:17,350
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Exactly. It's more normal for them to be much further out in the wilderness.</font>

122
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:26,350
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">But because of dragon - Stormterror - has been around a lot more recently, our orchards have been destroyed and the local market has been affected as well.</font> 

123
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:34,850
