124
00:14:34,950 --> 00:14:39,450
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>So these annoying creatures have been getting closer and closer to the city?</i>

125
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:44,850
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Exactly. That said, clearing this camp helped make the area a little vit safer.</font>

126
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:50,450
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Come with me! A responsible knight must make sure to see you to the city safely.</font> 

127
00:14:56,350 --> 00:14:59,050
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Wow! This will coming handy!</font>

128
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:29,000
