<b>Lynn (Adventurer):</b> Oh, are you travelers from around here as well?

131
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:45,350
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Nom we just happen to be passing by. *sniff* *sniff* What are you cooking? Smells good!</i>

