<b>Paimon:</b> <i>But... the city folk dont't look too cheery.</i>

161
00:19:03,850 --> 00:19:08,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Everyone's been put out of place by Stormterror recently.</font>

