<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Jean?</i>

164
00:19:14,800 --> 00:19:20,500
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Acting Grand Master of the Knights of Favonius - Jean, Defender of Mondstadt.</font>

165
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:25,350
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">With Jean on our side, surely even the vicious Stormterror will be no match for us.</font>

166
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:25,950
<b>Pasichnik:</b> (I hope she knows something about the God of Anemo)

167
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:31,050
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Befire I take you guys to the Knights of Favonius Headquaters, I have a present for you, Pasichnik</font>
(Оу май... гублюсь в здогадках шо це може бути... ги-ги-ги...)

168
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:34,800
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">It's a reward for helping me clear out that hilichurl camp.</font>
(Я уважно слухаю...)

169
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:39,150
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>He-Hey! Why doesn't Paimon get a reward?</i>
(Паймон, не лізь. Тут хтивства накльовуються.)

170
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:42,900
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Ahh... Because this reward is useless to you, Paimon.</font>
(А я про шо. Паймон, звали.)

171
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:48,650
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">But I'll treat you to a traditional Mondstadt delicacy - Sticky Honey Roast.</font>
(У-у-у... "Липка медова прожарка"... давай відкинемо евфемізми і ближче до діла.)

172
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:51,000
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Sticky Honey Roast!</i>
(Стоп! У цьому й Паймон прийматиме участь?)

173
00:19:51,250 --> 00:19:58,750
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Come with me, we'll head to the city's ahh... <b>high ground</b>.</font>
(СТОП! Це ще й привселюдно буде?)

174
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:31,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">This used to be a bustling street... But with so many Stormterror attacks recently, the usual crowds are nowhere to be seen.</font>
(І через це ти вирішила зі мною таке зробити - аби людей розважити?)

175
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:38,100
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Except for the local tavern near the city wall over there. They haven't been affected. If anything, their business is better than ever.</font>

176
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:55,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">So, the present I want to give you is...</font>
(Ну!...)

177
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:57,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">A <b>Wind Glider</b>!</font>
(... почуваюсь розчарованим!)

178
00:21:57,500 --> 00:22:02,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Outriders use them to ride the wind, and people of Mondstadt love using them too.</font>

179
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:07,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">I brought you here to give it to you so you can expirience it right away!</font>

180
00:22:07,050 --> 00:22:10,750
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Oh, you're really excited about these wind gliders, huh!</i>

181
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:15,340
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Well that's because the wind is the heart and soul of Mondstadt!</font>

182
00:22:15,450 --> 00:22:19,850
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Alrighty then, enough talk! Let's give it a whirl!</font>

183
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:23,900
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">It's easy to use, but you still need to pay attention to my instructions.</font>

184
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,500
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">The sky...</font>

185
00:23:56,950 --> 00:24:00,000
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Huh? How are you staying afloat like this with just a Wind Glider?</i>

186
00:24:01,850 --> 00:24:04,750
<font color="green">I'm preventing your fall with the power of a thousand winds.</font>

187
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:11,750
<font color="green>Now, concentrate. See yourself grasping the wind. Harness its energy.</font>

188
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,500
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Who... who sad that!?</i>

189
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:05,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">A-Are you hurt?</font>

190
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:18,000
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">You've actually got the power to go up against the dragon...</font>

191
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:22,450
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Are you a new ally... or a new storm?</font>

192
00:25:25,250 --> 00:25:28,900
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Stormterror... is attaking Mondstadt itself!</font>

193
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:32,650
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Kaeya, Pasichnik, you've come at the right time. We must...</font>

194
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:37,950
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Hold on, Amber. Are you perhaps forgetting to introduce us?</font>

195
00:25:38,350 --> 00:25:43,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Oh... right. This is Kaeya, our Cavalry Capitan.</font>

196
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:47,000
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">These two are travelers from afar, Pasichnik and Paimon.</font>

197
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:51,250
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">(From afar? Is that all we know of them?)</font>

198
00:25:51,450 --> 00:25:53,600
<b><font color="red">Amber:</font></b> <font color="red">Long story short...</font>

199
00:25:58,750 --> 00:26:03,900
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">I see. Welcome to Montdstadt - though you haven't arrived at the best of times, I'm afraid.</font>

200
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:08,000
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">I understand the anguish of being separated from family.</font>

201
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:11,900
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">I'm not really sure why you're looking for the Anemo God...</font>

202
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:14,850
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">But everyone has their secrets, right?</font>

203
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:19,100
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Haha, relax! I won't press you for more.</font>

204
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:27,000
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">First and foremost, on behalf of the Knights of Favonius, I would like to extend our thanks to your help just now.</font>

205
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:27,500
<b>Pasichnik:</b> Well, we couldn't just leave the situation to fester.

206
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:34,000
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Your fight to defend the city against the dragon just now was witnessed by no small number of citizens.</font>

207
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:41,950
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">The Acting Grand Master of the Knights of Favonius is also very interested in meeting you, and formally invites you both to <b>our headquarters</b></font>

208
00:27:20,950 --> 00:27:25,000
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>This seems to be the <b>Knights of Favonius Headquarters</b>. Let's head in.</i>

209
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:46,700
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Jean, what's the hurry? I thought we agreed to meet them here.</font>

210
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:51,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">There have been sightings of Stormterror outside the city. Once we met, we must...</font>

211
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:56,600
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Relax. I'll lend a hand when the time comes.</font>

212
00:27:57,100 --> 00:27:59,950
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Jean, I've brought them.</font>

213
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:09,100
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">...And once it was over I brought them straight here.</font>

214
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:15,950
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">Montstad welcomes you, windborne travelers.</font>

215
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:23,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">I am Jean, Acting Grand master of the Knights of Favonius. This is Lisa, our resident Librarian.</font>

216
00:28:23,125 --> 00:28:26,850
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Oh! Are you sweeties here to help us out?</font>

217
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:31,100
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">You're both so adorable!</font>
(Пасічник, вона точно тебе хоче. Це не як той раз з Ембер)

218
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:34,000
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Sadly, the timing is regrettable...</font>

219
00:28:34,150 --> 00:28:39,950
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Storterror has caused quite a ruckus in the region since its recent resurgence.</font>

220
00:28:40,050 --> 00:28:46,950
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Simply put, Montstardt's elemental sphere and ley lines are now akin to a yarn ball in the paws of a kitten.</font>

221
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:53,950
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">For a mage, it couldn't get much worse. My skin is one elemental particle away from full-blown breakout.</font>

222
00:28:54,000 --> 00:29:02,950
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">If it weren't this interference, the Knights of Favonious would have better ways to help you than just putting up missing person posters.</font>

223
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:09,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">We simply ask that you repose in Mondstadt while we help you seek out your sister.</font>

224
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:10,000
<b>Pasichnik:</b> I realy should help out as well.

225
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:12,000
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Paimon will help you too!</i>

226
00:29:12,050 --> 00:29:15,000
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Good. In that case we need a plan.</font>

229
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:21,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">With Stormterror now directly attaking Mondstadt, we may have an opportunity to cut this problem off at source.</font>

230
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:26,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">Lisa has revealed the sources of Stormterror's power with her detection magic.</font>
(Пасічник, а така магія представлена в грі як механіка?)

231
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:29,000
<b><font color="blue">Kaeya:</font></b> <font color="blue">Is that so?</font>

232
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:32,000
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">They're located in the abandoned <b>Four Winds' Temples</b></font>

233
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:39,000
<b><font color="purple">Lisa:</font></b> <font color="purple">Stormterror's ability to whip up these kinds of storms can be attributed to it drawing power from the temples.</font>

234
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:42,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">Our objective is to deal with <b>three</b> of the four temples.</font>

235
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:46,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">I trust everyone understands why we are only dealing with three/.</font>

236
00:29:46,150 --> 00:29:48,500
<b>Paimon:</b> <i>Paimon doesn't.</i>

237
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:49,250
<b>Pasichnik:</b> We'll ask later...

238
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">Knights of Favonius, time is against us.</font>

239
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:57,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">The storm is rampant. There is no point in maintaining a defensive position.</font>

240
00:29:57,000 --> 00:30:03,000
<b><font color="beige">Jean:</font></b> <font color="beige">Alright. We need to take initiative and act before the situation escalates.</font>

